            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 1,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1415032267,
            "creation_date": 1415032267,
            "body": "<p>Remove the semi colon<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>for (index = 0; index &lt; allowed.length - 1; index++);\n                                                    ^\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>which is terminating the for loop. The following code block is a standalone block which is executed only once<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 26718589,
